    "title": "Whiskers and the Crystal Jungle",
    "genre": "cartoon",
    "hook": "Whiskers spots golden light flickering between jungle vines at a mossy forest entrance.",
    "setup": "Whiskers the cat and Sage the fox enter a sunlit jungle path full of wonder.",
    "conflict": "The trail splits, the ground trembles, and the glow disappears behind ancient stones.",
    "discovery": "Ancient ruins reveal carved symbols that pulse when Sage touches the stone.",
    "escalation": "The ground shakes as roots trap them unless they reach the hidden chamber.",
    "climax": "Whiskers must choose courage over fear to carry the spark to safety.",
    "resolution": "A glowing crystal chamber blooms with light and opens a safe path home.",
    "ending_cta": "Follow for more magical adventures with Whiskers and Sage.",
    "scene_progression": [
      "Discovery: Sunlit jungle trail with vines, moss, and golden dust motes at the forest entrance (forest entrance)",
      "Escalation: Crumbling stone arches covered in moss and glowing carved symbols (ancient ruins)",
      "Reward: Underground crystal cavern pulsing with warm amber light and floating sparkles (hidden glowing chamber)"
    ],
